  "solution": "def solution(a : list) -> int:\n    sm = sum(a[::2]) - sum(a[1::2])\n    mn = min(a[::2])\n    mx = max(a[1::2])\n    return max(sm, sm + 2 * mx - 2 * mn)\n",
